# Excel Data Analysis Project

## Overview

This project focuses on analyzing structured data using Microsoft Excel to generate meaningful insights and visualizations.

## Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables
* Charts

## Key Insights

* Identified trends and patterns in the dataset
* Created summaries using pivot tables
* Visualized data using charts for better understanding

## Features

* Data cleaning and preprocessing
* Interactive Excel dashboard
* Insight generation from raw data
